{"tid":917040,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣做咩都好撚謹慎","createTime":"2018-11-26T06:18:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-26T09:55:27.000Z","uid":7628,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5b2e1bf0e4942b2450166f268e212771cf2e0052","tid":917040,"uid":7628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T06:18:21.000Z","msg":"由細到大 我做每一件事都會諗五六次先做<br />\n<br />\n例如同人講野前會不斷諗用咩開場白，用乜連接詞，咩位用咩語速咁 之類 好謹慎，唔想出錯<br />\n<br />\n同埋臨覺時 上到床個腦會不斷plan第二日嘅行程 例如幾點要起到身 幾點要上到車 但好神奇嘅地方就係我完全唔駛教鬧鐘都可以自然醒到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只要訓前不斷諗 第朝一定會起到（大概十分鐘誤差）<br />\n<br />\n有冇人同我一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實係咪病嘅一種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一直都唔知要睇邊種醫生"},{"pid":"61362f1412e44e2d5ad171aa1bbc2277c7bf6f6c","tid":917040,"uid":162316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T06:22:41.000Z","msg":"差唔多但無你咁嚴重<br />\n唔知好事定壞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb8f1856faeda733baa8574208e2eabad88ee9e8","tid":917040,"uid":198810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T06:24:08.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dcff89e5be9ced70e7d0850c2f4518ab1a4e3f3","tid":917040,"uid":7628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61362f1412e44e2d5ad171aa1bbc2277c7bf6f6c","tid":917040,"uid":162316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T06:22:41.000Z","msg":"差唔多但無你咁嚴重<br />\n唔知好事定壞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T06:33:44.000Z","msg":"好驚自己有咩暗病<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd90ce6cb5746088551f6570060d65249473e909","tid":917040,"uid":7628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T06:39:55.000Z","msg":"其實有時都好辛苦<br />\n訓上床要起碼半個鐘至一個鐘先訓得著"},{"pid":"1c1a7ad41cbc707f01e9193940bdfdf3260beff9","tid":917040,"uid":199675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T09:55:27.000Z","msg":"有時會 但無樓豬講到咁誇張 但我覺得係好事嚟 只要唔到過份咗"}]}